#📊 Databricks Advanced AI Challenge – End-to-End ML Lakehouse Pipeline

**🚀 Project Overview**
This repository documents my 14-day journey through the Databricks Advanced AI Challenge, where I built a complete Machine Learning Lakehouse pipeline using PySpark, Delta Lake, and MLflow.
The goal of this project was to design an end-to-end data and ML system that starts from raw event data and produces both predictive insights and personalized recommendations.

Over 14 days, the project evolved from simple data transformations into a full pipeline covering:
Data ingestion
Feature engineering
Machine learning training
Experiment tracking
Batch inference
Recommendation systems
Performance optimization
Data versioning
System architecture design
